name: Me myself and I
description: I see myself as a versatile person who’s mastering different professions. Now I’m a photographer. Through photography I want to convey my thoughts, inner world and manifesto. I like to show the beauty of women. I like to transmit through the photograph of great directors and artists. I love the visual component of photography. I like that the photo often does not make sense, but is simply a beautiful picture. Beauty in everything and I want you to see it with me!
